# Duplication Detection Module
#
# Analyzes codebase for duplicate code using token-based similarity detection.
# Provides configurable thresholds, ignore patterns, and detailed reporting
# of code clones and structural duplications.
#
# Public API:
#   - use compiler.tools.duplicate_check.main.{run_duplication_check, print_duplication_summary}
#   - use compiler.tools.duplicate_check.analyzer.{analyze_duplicates}
#   - use compiler.tools.duplicate_check.config.{DuplicationConfig}
#   - use compiler.tools.duplicate_check.types.{DuplicateReport, CodeClone}
#
# Internal Components:
#   - Token-based analysis
#   - Similarity detection
#   - Report formatting
#   - Configuration management

# All submodules are automatically available through the module system.
# Uses token-based similarity detection (not line-based) to identify
# structural duplications.

